data.name: Chubby Stick™ Sculpting Highlight
data.description: Luminous cream highlighting stick with light-reflecting optics brings your best features forward. Long-wearing, oil-free.

data.name: Chubby Stick™ Sculpting Contour
data.description: Creamy contouring stick creates the illusion of depth; makes areas appear to recede. Long-wearing, oil-free.

data.name: Blended Face Powder and Brush
data.description: Clinique's signature blended powder. Loose, lightweight texture is right for every type of skin. Sets and perfects makeup, makes pores seem to disappear. Airy, skin-hugging formula delivers a reliably flawless finish.

data.name: Up-lighting™ Liquid Illuminator
data.description: Sheer, lightweight liquid instantly illuminates skin. Highlights and contours cheeks, brow bones, or gives face an allover glow. Glides on to create a natural-looking luminosity. Perfect for all skin types and tones. Oil-free.

data.name: True Bronze™ Pressed Powder Bronzer
data.description: Lightweight powder bronzer creates a natural-looking, sun-kissed radiance. Blends, builds easily to your desired level of bronze. Perfect for on-the-go glow. Long-wearing. Oil-free.

data.name: Uplighting Illuminating Powder
data.description: This sheer illuminating powder with soft-focus pigments flatters skin with a candle-lit glow of radiance. Wear it alone, as a finishing powder after foundation, or as a highlighter only where you want it. In 3 luminous shades.

data.name: Sun-Kissed Face Gelee Complexion Multitasker
data.description: An instant pick-me-up for skin. Sheer, oil-free gel creates a warm, healthy glow. Appropriate for all skin types and tones. Ophthalmologist Tested.

data.name: PRO FILT'R - Soft Matte Longwear Foundation
data.description: A soft matte, longwear foundation with buildable, medium to full coverage, in a boundary-breaking range of 40 shades.

data.name: Sculptionary™ Cheek Contouring Palette
data.description: Versatile cheek sculpting compact with natural-looking shades that blend and build beautifully. Use each separately to colour, contour, highlight. Or swirl them together for a quick easy glow. Use mid-toned shade as a blush, deep-toned shade to contour, lightest shade to highlight. For a quick, easy glow swirl brush over entire palette and dust over apples of cheeks. Long-wearing, oil-free.

data.name: Blushing Blush™ Powder Blush
data.description: Silky formula sweeps effortlessly over cheekbones to create a natural look. Fresh, jet-milled colour builds and blends beautifully to desired intensity with custom sculpting brush. Long-wearing, colour-true. Oil-free.

data.name: Cheek Pop™
data.description: Vibrant yet natural-looking cheek colour that looks virtually powderless. In a silky smooth, stay-true formula with shades for every skin tone. That just-pinched look, simply effortless.

product_colors.colour_name: Clinique + Jonathan Adler: Cheek Pop in Peach Pop
Clinique + Jonathan Adler: Cheek Pop in Plum Pop

data.name: Soft-Pressed Powder Blusher
data.description: Warm, natural-looking powder blush for all skins. Sheer, buildable colour gives cheeks a radiant glow. Silky, fresh finish, too. Wide range of shades, from subtle to vibrant. Comes with brush applicator.

data.name: Chubby Stick™ Cheek Colour Balm
data.description: Creamy, mistake-proof cheek colour creates a healthy-looking glow in an instant. Oil-free.

data.name: CliniqueFIT™  Lip + Cheek Flush
data.description: It’s like a post-workout glow without the workout. Sheer gel adds a healthy-looking touch of colour to lips and cheeks. Fade resistant. Oil-free.

data.name: Chubby™ Plump & Shine Liquid Lip Plumping Gloss
data.description: This light-reflecting, high-shine gloss enhances the appearance of lips, making them appear plump and smooth. Moisturizes, wears for hours. Feels refreshing and cool upon application. Dermatologist Tested. Allergy Tested. 100% Fragrance Free.

data.name: Quickliner™ For Lips
data.description: All-day lip liner. Use to line and define lips or smooth all over lips before lipstick application for extended wear. Non-drying formula helps keep lipstick in place. Prevents lipstick from feathering and bleeding. No sharpening required.

data.name: Quickliner™ For Lips Intense
data.description: Silky formula glides on and wears all day. Use it to define the lip line or fill in lips pre-lipstick application. Non-drying formula prevents lipstick from feathering and bleeding. No sharpening required.

data.name: Almost Lipstick
data.description: Transparent pigment merges with the unique, natural tone of your lips to create something wonderful and yours alone. Sheer, glossy. Emollient-rich and very lightweight.

data.name: Butter Shine™ Lipstick
data.description: The creamiest, richest, smoothest lip colour you can imagine. Our revolutionary gel formula delivers the shine of a gloss, the comfort of a lipstick. Drenches lips in moist, lush colour that glides on buttery-soft, feels luxuriously smooth.

data.name: Chubby Stick Intense™ Moisturizing Lip Colour Balm
data.description: Tempt lips with a soft cushion of colour that's not quite sheer, not quite opaque-just the perfect happy medium. Loaded with mango and shea butters so lips feel comfortably soft and smooth. Ten vibrant shades in all.

data.name: Long Last Soft Matte Lipstick
data.description: Long-wearing formula keeps its just-applied look for hours. Non-drying, non-feathering. Full coverage, velvety, soft matte finish.

data.name: Long Last Lipstick
data.description: Longest-wearing formula. Keeps its just-applied look for hours. Won't feather, creep, stain or dry out.

data.name: Instant Lift For Brows
data.description: Two-in-one automatic brow pencil and pearlized highlighter duo creates a contrast and definition that give eyes a virtual lift. First, fill in and shape brows with long-wearing natural-looking pencil. Then optically 'boost' brow arches with universal highlighter shade just below brow hairs.

data.name: Superfine Liner For Brows
data.description: Convenient pencil creates perfectly defined, natural-looking brows. Ultra-fine tip fills even the smallest gaps with precise, hair-like strokes. Automatically self-sharpens; glides on without skipping or tugging. Colour lasts all day.

data.name: Pretty Easy Brow Palette
data.description: Deluxe brow kit features natural-looking brow powder, powder highlighter, tinted brow fixative plus 4 applicator tips for a precise touch. Includes easy-to-follow illustrated how-tos.

data.name: Brow Keeper
data.description: A two-in-one tool for perfectly arched brows. Pencil end shades and shapes with a creamy formula that goes on, holds on. At the other end, a fine-tuned brush keeps brows impeccably groomed. Apply lightly for a natural look. Go heavier for pure glam.

data.name: Just Browsing Brush-On Styling Mousse
data.description: 24-hour long-wearing brow mousse tints, tames, fills-in even the sparsest brows. Mini applicator brushes on natural-looking colour that resists smudging, sweat and humidity. Water-resistant, too. Ophthalmologist Tested. Allergy Tested. 100% Fragrance Free.

data.name: Brow Shaper
data.description: Fine pressed powder, special brush. Soft, natural colours fill in and perfect brows with no harsh lines.

data.name: Clinique Pop Liquid™ Matte Lip Colour + Primer
data.description: Lightweight liquid lipstick covers lips with lush pigment and a modern matte finish. Wears all day. Moisturizing formula with built-in primer provides a smooth, even glide so lips feel as fresh as they look.

data.name: Chubby Stick Baby Tint™ Moisturizing Lip Colour Balm
data.description: A bit of colour, a hefty helping of moisture. These sheers bloom on contact to bring out your lips' natural tone. The colour is different for everyone.

data.name: Clinique + Jonathan Adler: Pop Lip Colour + Primer
data.description: An exclusive collection of luminous Clinique Pop™ lipsticks by Jonathan Adler. Includes 3 limited-edition shades inspired by his favorite destinations: Palm Beach Pop, Capri Pop and Santorini Pop.  Jewel-like lipsticks in bold, saturated colors look as pretty on your lips as they do on your vanity. “The domes of Lucite are inspired by my Globo collection—glowing and glamorous. Just like Lip Pop,” says Adler.

data.name: Different Lipstick
data.description: Different because of its smooth, comfortable feel. Moderate coverage in a remarkable range of shades, from cream to pearl. Every one packed with rich emollients.

data.name: Clinique Pop™ Lacquer Lip Colour + Primer
Clinique Pop Glaze™ Sheer Lip Colour + Primer
Chubby Stick™ Moisturizing Lip Colour Balm
data.description: Super-nourishing balm is loaded with mango and shea butters. Just what dry, delicate lips need to feel comfortably soft and smooth. Natural-looking lip tints have a subtle sheen.

data.name: Clinique Pop™ Matte Lip Colour + Primer
data.description: Weightless yet pigment-saturated formula hugs lips with 8 hours of creamy matte comfort. Built-in primer helps smooth lips for an easy, even glide every time.

data.name: Clinique Pop™ Lip Colour + Primer
data.description: Luxurious yet weightless formula merges bold, saturated colour with a smoothing primer. Glides on effortlessly to a modern-velvet finish. Colour stays true, keeps lips comfortably moisturized for 8 hours. Allergy Tested. 100% Fragrance Free.

data.name: Clinique Pop™ Lip Shadow Cushion Matte Lip Powder
data.description: Clinique Pop™ Lip Shadow is a weightless matte powder that delivers bold, highly pigmented lip color.
